<div style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: #111; font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">Welcome to OllaZen</h1>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Hi <%= @user.name.presence || 'there' %>!</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Your provider account for <strong><%= @business_name %></strong> is set up. You can now manage your business, services, and bookings from your dashboard.</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">Once our team has reviewed your profile, your listing will be visible to customers. We'll notify you when you're approved.</p>
  <p style="color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">— The OllaZen team</p>
</div>
